'''Central multitasking units''' were devices used aboard [[Starship/Legends|spacecraft]] that allowed a single [[Computer/Legends|computer]] to control the functions of a number of diverse peripheral devices. These included, but were not limited to food preparation units, life support, communications, and entertainment systems. They were known to be used on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Orbital Solar Energy Transfer Satellite|Mirror Stations]].

